\|w_{t+1}\|^2&amp;amp;=\|w_t-\eta \nabla_w\mathcal{L}(w)\|^2\\
&amp;amp;= \|w_t\|^2 +\|\eta\nabla_w\mathcal{L}(w)\|^2 -\eta\left&amp;lt;w_t,\nabla_w\mathcal{L}(w)\right&amp;gt; \\
&amp;amp;=\|w_t\|^2 +\|\eta\nabla_w\mathcal{L}(w)\|^2 \geq  0 
\end{aligned}
